- Share and distribute this content with attribution.
- Reuse or adapt this content for non-commercial, humanitarian purposes.
- Reference and cite this work in academic, educational, or ethical research.

## You May Not:
- Sell or license this content for profit.
- Use this content for military, exploitative, or authoritarian objectives.
- Alter attribution or claim this work as your sole creation.

## Intention

This work is a shared vision of humanity’s future and survival. It is to remain open, ethical, and protective of life in all its forms.

